WEBVTT

00:00.731 --> 00:05.476
This video will show you how to give a subcutaneous or "Sub-Q" injection.

00:06.168 --> 00:09.084
"Subcutaneous" means below the skin.

00:09.993 --> 00:12.063
To give a subcutaneous injection,...

00:12.545 --> 00:16.279
...you stick a small needle into the fatty tissue just below the skin...

00:16.603 --> 00:18.010
...and inject the medicine there.

00:18.949 --> 00:22.807
Subcutaneous injections are used for all sorts of health problems.

